ZH: 他肆意地破坏了公共财产。
EN: He willfully destroyed public property.

ZH: 她肆意地驾驶着超速。
EN: She drove recklessly over the speed limit.

ZH: 孩子们肆意地在房间里乱跑。
EN: The children were running around the room carelessly.

ZH: 他们肆意地浪费了水。
EN: They wasted water without any consideration.

ZH: 媒体肆意地夸大了事实。
EN: The media exaggerated the facts freely.

ZH: 他们肆意地欺负弱者。
EN: They bullied the weak with impunity.

ZH: 政治家们肆意地滥用权力。
EN: Politicians abused their power without restraint.

ZH: 这家餐厅肆意地提高食物价格。
EN: This restaurant arbitrarily increased the food prices.

ZH: 他肆意地践踏了别人的权益。
EN: He trampled on others' rights wantonly.

ZH: 她肆意地拒绝了我的邀请。
EN: She rejected my invitation without hesitation.

ZH: 他肆意地改动了我的作品。
EN: He made unauthorized changes to my work audaciously.

ZH: 犯罪分子肆意地盗窃了珍贵的艺术品。
EN: The criminals stole precious artworks recklessly.

ZH: 学生们肆意地抄袭了作业。
EN: The students shamelessly plagiarized the homework.

ZH: 媒体肆意地扭曲了事实。
EN: The media distorted the facts maliciously.

ZH: 她肆意地删除了公司的重要文件。
EN: She arbitrarily deleted important files of the company.

ZH: 这个团队肆意地忽视了安全规定。
EN: This team deliberately ignored safety regulations.

ZH: 他肆意地侮辱了他的同事。
EN: He insulted his colleague willfully.

ZH: 这家公司肆意地裁员以减少成本。
EN: This company laid off employees arbitrarily to cut costs.

ZH: 他们肆意地破坏了环境。
EN: They destroyed the environment wantonly.

ZH: 她肆意地试图掌控他人的生活。
EN: She arrogantly attempted to control other people's lives.
